Derby-229: Return first matching column name, instead of last column in the select list for getter methods.
Column names supplied to getter [updater] methods are case insensitive. If a select list contains the same column more than once, the first instance of the column will be returned [updated]. Derby returns or updates the last column in the select list, not the first.
